tag-enjoining-good","tag-manners-adab","tag-mercy-al-rahmah","tag-rights-al-huquq"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8yE","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":5423,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/20\/adab-children-elders\/","url_meta":{"origin":32900,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Manners: Respectful to elders, merciful to children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever does not show mercy to our young ones, or acknowledge the rights of our elders, he is not one of us.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4943 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19702,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/08\/06\/ummah-not-true-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":32900,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ummah: No true Muslim violates their rights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 6, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe is not part of my nation who neither honors our elders, nor has mercy on our young ones, nor acknowledges the rights of our scholars.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 22755 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17213,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/17\/elders-honored-old-age\/","url_meta":{"origin":32900,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Elders: Whoever honors elders will be honored in old age","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 17, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo youth honors his elders but that Allah will appoint someone to honor him in his old age.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2022 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35142,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/01\/when-to-give-up\/","url_meta":{"origin":32900,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Evil: When to abandon enjoining good?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, when should we give up enjoining good and forbidding evil?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen there appears among you the same as the nations which came before you.\u201d We said, \u201cO Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_conte